	<h1 id="welcome-to-datin-s-playground-">Welcome to Datin's Playground!</h1>
	<p>New to the server?  Want steps to follow in order to join in on the fun?  Then look no further!</p>
	<p>To connect to whatever game is currently running, just connect to game.datyedyeguy.net in either Hidden or Garry's Mod.</p>
	<p>If you have any questions, email me at <a href="mailto:game@datyedyeguy.net">game@datyedyeguy.net</a></p>
	<h2 id="how-to-setup-the-hidden-source">How to Setup The Hidden: Source</h2>
	<ul>
	<li>Install <a href="http://store.steampowered.com/about">Steam</a></li>
	<li>Install <a href="http://store.steampowered.com/app/220/" title="Half-Life 2 on Steam">Half-Life 2</a></li>
	<li>Install <a href="steam://install/215/" title="Source SDK Base 2006 on Steam">Source SDK Base 2006</a></li>
	<li>Download and install the <a href="http://www.hidden-source.com/downloads.htm">Hidden Client Installer</a></li>
	<li>Download the following maps and extract them in the following directories</li>
	<ol>
		<li><a href="http://hs.gamebanana.com/maps/download/16347">hdn_psychiatry</a> => %STEAM%\steamapps\sourcemods\hidden\maps</li>
		<li><a href="http://hs.gamebanana.com/maps/download/16345">hdn_deadmeatb4b</a> => %STEAM%\steamapps\sourcemods\hidden</li>
		<li><a href="http://hs.gamebanana.com/maps/download/14962">hdn_castle_b4</a> => %STEAM%\steamapps\sourcemods\hidden\maps</li>
	</ol>
	</ul>
	<p>Now you should have an entry in your Steam Library for "Hidden: Source Beta 4b".  If you do, then you are all good to go!  Just connect to game.datyedyeguy.net to get your game on!</p>
	<p>I recommend playing through the tutorial to lean how the Hidden controls, along with reading through the <a href="http://www.hidden-source.com/downloads/manual.pdf">Manual</a> so that you aren't completely lost when you hop in.</p>
	<h2 id="how-to-setup-garry-s-mod">How to Setup Garry's Mod</h2>
	<ul>
	<li>Install <a href="http://store.steampowered.com/about">Steam</a></li>
	<li>Install <a href="http://store.steampowered.com/app/4000" title="Garry's Mod on Steam">Garry's Mod</a></li>
	<li>Install <a href="http://store.steampowered.com/app/240/" title="Counter-Strike: Source on Steam">Counter-Strike: Source</a><ul>
	<li>This is required due to maps on Garry's Mod using assets from Counter-Strike: Source.</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li>Subscribe to everything in <a href="http://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=349910372">Datin's Playground Collection</a> on Steam.<ul>
	<li>This will download any custom maps/sounds/etc when you next startup Garry's Mod</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	</ul>
	<p>Now, when you start up Garry's Mod, you should be able to connect to game.datyedyeguy.net and get your game on!</p>
